        <item>
            <title>Tesla Optimus Bot 機械人 2 代，行走速度快 30% + 較上代輕 22 磅</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/tesla-bot-2nd-gen-optimus-bot/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-bot-2nd-gen-optimus-bot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/tesla-bot-2nd-gen-optimus-bot/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 13:35:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Optimus Bot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Optimus Bot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人形機械人]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210306</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>半年前 Tesla 正式發佈旗下人形機械人 Tesla Bot 的示範影片（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/05/17/tesla-bot-now-can-walk-and-train-with-motion-capture-of-human/fun-tech/">相關報道</a>），沒料到事隔才半年， Tesla 就推出了第二代人型機械人— Optimus Bot。Optimus Bot 比上一代有很多改進，例如他可以深蹲、行走速度比上一代快了 30%、重量減輕了 22 磅，以及其肢體動作更加靈活。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130818-694x372.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130818-694x372.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130818-1280x686.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130818-768x411.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130818-1536x823.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130818.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>據《electrek》報道，Optimus Bot 可以替人類完成沈悶的重複性工序。Optimus Bot 能夠以兩足姿態平穩站立，而且其行走速度比上一代快了 30%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130845-694x372.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130845-694x372.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130845-1280x685.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130845-768x411.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130845-1536x822.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130845.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Optimus Bot 更可以 90 度深蹲</p><p>Optimus Bot 具有全新設計的手掌，全部手指均設有觸角感應，而且其靈敏度亦比上代大幅提升，可以處理雞蛋這類易碎物品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210310" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130829-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130829-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130829-1280x681.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130829-768x409.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130829-1536x817.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130829.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210309" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130858-694x370.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130858-694x370.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130858-1280x682.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130858-768x409.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130858-1536x818.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-130858.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210311" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-131940-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-131940-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-131940-1280x681.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-131940-768x409.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-131940-1536x817.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-12-13-131940.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>據《Torque News》引述 Tesla AI 團隊員工 Milan Kovac 指，這一代（Optimus Bot）實際上是人形機械人計劃開始後不到 2 年內發展出的第 3 代，比上一代更有效率。Milan Kovac 另外指 Tesla 上傳的示範影片沒有經過加速處理，而且沒有任何 CGI 動畫後製。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">BREAKING: Tesla has introduced Optimus Gen 2!</p><p>• Tesla designed actuators and sensors<br />• 2-Dof actuated neck<br />• Actuators integrated electronics &amp; harnessing<br />• 30% walk speed boost<br />• Foot force/torque sensing<br />• 22lb weight reduction<br />• and more <a href="https://t.co/zaXxZwNNWh">pic.twitter.com/zaXxZwNNWh</a></p><p>&mdash; Sawyer Merritt (@SawyerMerritt) <a href="https://twitter.com/SawyerMerritt/status/1734759100058050669?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 13, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.torquenews.com/14335/tesla-unveils-tesla-optimus-bot-generation-2-doing-squats-30-faster-walking-22-lb-weight">Torque News</a>、<a href="https://electrek.co/2023/12/12/tesla-unveils-optimus-gen-2-next-generation-humanoid-robot/">Electrek</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/SawyerMerritt/status/1734759100058050669">SawyerMerritt@X</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/tesla-bot-2nd-gen-optimus-bot/ai/">Tesla Optimus Bot 機械人 2 代，行走速度快 30% + 較上代輕 22 磅</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
