        <item>
            <title>港鐵推信用卡出入閘    12 月 23 日 Visa 率先登場</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/visa-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=visa-mtr</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/visa-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 11:32:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mtr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Visa]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港鐵]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210340</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">港鐵公司今（13 日）公佈，將於今年 12 月 23 日起，分階段推出感應式信用卡乘搭港鐵服務，乘客當日起可於特定的閘機使用 Visa 體驗新服務出閘，而明年第三季將涵蓋更多信用卡作支付。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210345 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07471-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今年 12 月 23 日起，分階段推出感應式信用卡乘搭港鐵服務</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">現時港鐵重鐵網絡（機場快綫車站除外）每個車站已配備起碼兩部提供感應式信用卡支付功能的出入閘機，較多旅客使用的車站則會有更多配備。新閘機貼有淺藍色標示，方便乘客辨認。12 月 23 日起，乘客使用感應式信用卡、扣賬卡或載有這兩項支付功能的裝置如手提電話及智能手錶等，在淺藍色閘機的信用卡讀卡器一拍便可出入閘，而可使用新支付功能的閘機亦會陸續增加。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210346 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07428-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲每個車站已配備起碼兩部提供感應式信用卡支付功能的出入閘機</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210347 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07433-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新閘機貼有淺藍色標示，方便乘客辨認</p><h2>實試入閘</h2><p>使用 Visa 信用卡及扣賬卡出入閘過程簡單，基本上與八達通一樣，只要將 Visa 信用卡及扣賬卡往感應器拍卡，乘客會聽到「嘟」一聲，閘門打門後，即可出入閘。而拍卡至出入閘時間與八達通相約，一拍即能過閘。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210348 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07485-4-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拍卡至出入閘時間與八達通相約，一拍即能過閘</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">隨著重鐵網絡的感應式信用卡支付服務接受 Visa 信用卡及扣賬卡，全部港鐵站客務中心亦已增加電子支付服務。信用卡支付的第二階段將於二零二四年第三季展開，更多信用卡可作電子支付。公司亦計劃最快於二零二六年在機場快綫更新閘機，同時提供感應式信用卡付費乘車服務，而整項自動收費系統資產更新計劃預計於二零二八年完成，屆時港鐵網絡的閘機會完成全面提升。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210403 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07499-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲信用卡支付的第二階段將於二零二四年第三季展開，更多信用卡可作電子支付。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/visa-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/">港鐵推信用卡出入閘    12 月 23 日 Visa 率先登場</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
